  <HuntersCovenant.label>猎人盟约</HuntersCovenant.label>
  <!-- EN: A gathering of hunterphages that was formed thousands of years ago. After the collapse of the Archadia Empire, the hunterphages were scattered through multiple star systems, drifting aimlessly and deprived of purpose. But their days of aimless drifting finally ended when a lone hunterphage, Julius Macragge, stood up and unified his scattered brothers and sisters in a single covenant, which was later named as the hunters covenant. The hunters covenant endured multiple trials, from pirate raids to mechanoid onslaughts, but at the very end they manage to establish a haven that can last through many years to come. -->
  <HuntersCovenant.description>一个形成于数千年前的猎食者群落。 阿卡迪亚帝国覆灭后，猎食者们散落于多个星系，漫无目的地漂泊，失去了生存目标。但当一名孤身一人的猎食者——朱利叶斯·麦克拉格挺身而出，将四散的兄弟姐妹们团结在一个盟约之下时，他们漫无目的的漂泊岁月终于画上了句号。该盟约后来被命名为“猎人盟约”。 “猎人盟约”历经了从海盗袭击到机械生命体猛攻的诸多考验，但最终他们成功建立了一处能够延续许多年的避难所。</HuntersCovenant.description>
